<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> والابتلاء:</span> <span class="c2">(أَحَسِبَ النَّاسُ أَنْ يُتْرَكُوا أَنْ يَقُولُوا آمَنَّا وَهُمْ لَا يُفْتَنُونَ)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٤ -<span class="c5"> والصدّ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَاحْذَرْهُمْ أَنْ يَفْتِنُوكَ عَنْ بَعْضِ ... )</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٥ -<span class="c5"> والجنون:</span> <span class="c2">(فَسَتُبْصِرُ وَيُبْصِرُونَ (٥)</span> بِأَيِّكُمُ الْمَفْتُونُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٦ -<span class="c5"> والعذاب:</span> <span class="c2">(فَإِذَا أُوذِيَ فِي اللَّهِ جَعَلَ فِتْنَةَ النَّاسِ كَعَذَابِ اللَّهِ)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٧ -<span class="c5"> والإحراق بالنار:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنَّ الَّذِينَ فَتَنُوا الْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ ثُمَّ لَمْ يَتُوبُوا)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٨ -<span class="c5"> والقتل:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنْ خِفْتُمْ أَنْ يَفْتِنَكُمُ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">(ذُوقُوا فِتْنَتَكُمْ)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٩ -<span class="c5"> والضلال:</span> <span class="c2">(وَمَنْ يُرِدِ اللَّهُ فِتْنَتَهُ)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span> و <span class="c2">(مَا أَنْتُمْ عَلَيْهِ بِفَاتِنِينَ)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١٠ -<span class="c5"> والشرك:</span> <span class="c2">(وَالْفِتْنَةُ أَشَدُّ مِنَ الْقَتْلِ)</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> <span class="c2">(وَقَاتِلُوهُمْ حَتَّى لَا تَكُونَ فِتْنَةٌ)</span> <span class="c2">(١١)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١١ -<span class="c5"> والكفر:</span> <span class="c2">(لَقَدِ ابْتَغَوُا الْفِتْنَةَ مِنْ قَبْلُ)</span> <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> و <span class="c2">(وَلَكِنَّكُمْ فَتَنْتُمْ أَنْفُسَكُمْ)</span> <span class="c2">(١٣)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>